longBusinessSummary: Jetblack Corp., through its subsidiaries, operates in the cannabis industry. The company is in the process of transferring ownership and locations for a Tier 1 Marijuana Producers Licenses with OLCC. The company has finalized an agreement to begin the process of transferring ownership and locations of an Oregon Marijuana Processors License. It also applied for other licenses with OLCC, such as an Oregon Marijuana Wholesale License. Jetblack Corp. was founded in 2002 and is based in Portland, Oregon.
